 George Best arrested again
London: Former Manchester United great George Best was arrested for drunk driving early on Friday, police said. Hes been charged with driving while over the alcohol limit, a police spokeswoman said. Last month he spent Christmas night in jail over an alleged assault but was freed without charge.  (REUTERS)  Copyright 
